SunSpotPuzzle Rails Server
==========================

The rails (http-)server for the SunSpot puzzle.

For instructions have a look at the github wiki (http://github.com/lukaselmer/sun_spot_puzzle/wiki).


Setup
=====

* Install ruby/rails (version 2.3.8)
* Copy and adjust database config file (see /config/database.yml.example)
* rake db:create
* rake db:migrate
* ruby script/server
